                "and 27Si recoils in S800 spectrograph was required"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A beam of radioactive 26Si ions was produced by",
                "projectile fragmentation of 150 MeV/A primary 36Ar",
                "beam. Secondary energy of 26Si ions was 30 MeV/A,",
                "beam purity was (60+-5) % and typical intensity",
                "approx. 1E+5 ions/s. Time of flight measrements",
                "upstream and downstream of the target allowed",
                "identification of incomming 26Si ions on event by",
                "event basis."
              ]
            }
